data.description: This quaint ranch style home has it all! With PAID FOR SOLAR PANELS, a huge screened in back patio, mature trees and its exceptional location on a quiet cul-de-sac inside of Wescott Plantation, you just can't beat it! Conveniently located just minutes from Joint Base Charleston, Charleston airport, Boeing, Bosch, shopping and entertainment, this 3 bed / 2 bath with a LARGE BONUS ROOM home will be sure to amaze! Inside you will find an open floor plan perfect for entertaining. The cozy family room can be found right off of the eat-in kitchen that boasts plenty of counter and cabinet space! The master bedroom has a trayed ceiling with a large walk-in closet and its own ensuite bath that features dual vanities and separate tub and walk-in shower.The two additional bedrooms are spacious and perfect for guests or children and share their own full bathroom. The huge bonus room found near the front of the home is great for a home office, kid's playroom, or anything else you can imagine! Outside you'll find the tranquil screened in back patio with an additional uncovered patio great for grilling that looks out to the backyard. Come take a look at this home today before it's gone!
